    public static interface Visitor.BlockStatementVisitor<R,​EX extends java.lang.Throwable>
extends Visitor.FieldDeclarationOrInitializerVisitor<R,​EX>
    The visitor for all kinds of Java.BlockStatements (statements that may appear with a block).
